sequenceDiagram
  participant FE as Frontend
  participant API as API
  participant W as Deploy Worker
  participant N as Netlify
  participant G as GSC
  participant DB as DB
  FE->>API: approve version
  API->>DB: save approval
  API->>W: queue deploy
  W->>DB: load approved version
  W->>W: build static site
  W->>N: deploy files
  N-->>W: deploy URL/status
  W->>W: update sitemap
  W->>G: submit/sync sitemap
  W->>DB: save deployment
